description: The creative inspiration of Atlantic Coin (ATC) comes from the establishment and creation of a chain industry alliance with Atlantic currency as the circulation medium and value anchor, and the use of "memory block chain" as the underlying technological support, in which "smart contract" will be maximized in the economic commonwealth. The memory block chain is open, transparent and can not be tampered with. It solves the persistent problem of information disclosure in traditional industries. At the same time, AT will increase cooperation with off-line entities, actively build industrial alliances of memory block chains, break through business barriers among enterprises, so as to establish a circulation platform of asset value among them. Yate coin has solved the problem of authorization of personal data by establishing a personal data authorization system, enabling personal data to be legally used on the Internet. Yate currency is also very positive for the market development and influence of digital products, and plays an indispensable role in protecting the rights and interests of producers and consumers. The total amount of Atlantic coins is 21 billion and will never be issued.
name: Atlantic Coin
